{"type":"message","id":"ecc80ad9","parentId":"bc224852","timestamp":"2026-05-31T06:10:23.236Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the cron jobs:\n\n1. **morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204** - this is the morning court cron job for 汀桑. It failed with timeout.\n\nBut wait, I see only two cron jobs listed under \"father\" agent: \"faye-pending-urges\" and \"faye-dreaming\". The morning court cron job might be under \"son\" agent or it might have a different name. Let me check - the error message says the job name is \"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\" and it timed out.\n\nActually, looking at the cron list, I don't see a \"morningcourt\" job in the list. This could be because the cron job is assigned to a different agent (son). Let me check.\n\nAlso, looking at the dreaming cron job (f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9), it also had the same error - \"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)\". Both timed out during the model call phase.\n\nThe root cause is straightforward: the model call timed out. This could be because:\n1. The DeepSeek model response took too long (> timeoutSeconds)\n2. The timeoutSeconds setting is too low for the amount of work being done\n\nLooking at the dreaming job, it has timeoutSeconds: 300 (5 minutes), and it ran for ~302 seconds before timing out. The morningcourt job probably has a similar or shorter timeout.\n\nLet me check what the morning court cron looks like - it was probably set up by 汀桑 himself. Let me look at the son agent's cron jobs.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Tj6mSOIh5ZiGSMGF5QYw5579","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","agentId":"son"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"list\", \"agentId\": \"son\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2609,"output":443,"cacheRead":22656,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":382,"totalTokens":25708,"cost":{"input":0.00036526,"output":0.00012404,"cacheRead":0.000634368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001123668}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780207819823,"responseId":"b78703aa-4018-49e0-ac6e-cc5f2c89bc9d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc0fe827","parentId":"ecc80ad9","timestamp":"2026-05-31T06:10:23.778Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Tj6mSOIh5ZiGSMGF5QYw5579","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678\",\n      \"agentId\": \"son\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204\",\n      \"name\": \"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1779997894311,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"[morningcourt] sender_id=6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, trigger briefing generation\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n        \"accountId\": \"bot1\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780272000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780185600025,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 122761,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)\",\n        \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n          \"summary\": \"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)\",\n          \"entries\": [\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780185722785,\n              \"source\": \"cron-setup\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)\"\n            }\n          ]\n        },\n        \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)\",\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780185722786\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 1,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 1,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null,\n  \"deliveryPreviews\": {\n    \"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    }\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678","agentId":"son","sessionKey":"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204","name":"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779997894311,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 8 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[morningcourt] sender_id=6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, trigger briefing generation","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","accountId":"bot1"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780272000000,"lastRunAtMs":1780185600025,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":122761,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":1,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastError":"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)","lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)","entries":[{"ts":1780185722785,"source":"cron-setup","severity":"error","message":"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)"}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)","lastErrorReason":"timeout"},"updatedAtMs":1780185722786}],"total":1,"offset":0,"limit":1,"hasMore":false,"next