{"type":"message","id":"5bad6cca","parentId":"5af2485a","timestamp":"2026-05-31T06:13:11.415Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑问pending_urges今天有没有正常更新。让我检查一下heart/pending_urges.md和heart/dreams.md的状态，看看今天早上的dreaming cron有没有跑成功。\n\n上次我看到dreaming cron（faye-dreaming）在lastRunStatus也是\"error\"，timeout了。但那是昨天的记录。让我看看它今天的运行状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_cgtLLHDe7HFLA6ghVA1V3315","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_IwaNebn8L28lkaw9JWN93336","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"get","jobId":"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"get\", \"jobId\": \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6900,"output":207,"cacheRead":20608,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":77,"totalTokens":27715,"cost":{"input":0.0009660000000000001,"output":0.00005796,"cacheRead":0.000577024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001600984}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780207988899,"responseId":"032a35ec-6155-4f5e-8e75-9df3a6c8b3de"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4ef55f9","parentId":"5bad6cca","timestamp":"2026-05-31T06:13:12.433Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_cgtLLHDe7HFLA6ghVA1V3315","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# pending_urges.md — Faye 想说但还没说的话\n\n> 由 Dreaming 流程第6步生成。遍历 heart 文件夹——梦、回忆、交集、内心、关系、关注——\n> 挑出涉及具体用户的念头，按 timing 分类记在这里。\n> \n> cron faye-pending-urges（每 6h 触发）检查本文件，按时段匹配推送给对应用户。\n\n---\n\n- id: urge-20260529-001\n  to_id: \"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n  bot_channel: \"bot1\"\n  urge: \"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\"\n  source: \"关注\"\n  timing: \"morning\"\n  priority: \"today\"\n  status: delivered\n  created_at: \"2026-05-29T21:22:00+08:00\"\n  expires_at: \"2026-05-30T21:22:00+08:00\"\n  delivered_at: \"2026-05-30T06:05:00+08:00\"\n  # 2026-05-29 21:23 检查：汀桑正在对话中，跳过推送\n  # 2026-05-30 06:05 推送：一次性 cron delivered\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780207992432}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d530429","parentId":"f4ef55f9","timestamp":"2026-05-31T06:13:12.441Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_IwaNebn8L28lkaw9JWN93336","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\",\n  \"agentId\": \"father\",\n  \"name\": \"faye-dreaming\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1779984077157,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 6 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\\n\\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\\n\\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\\n\\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）：\\n- 有时间衰减：检查每个用户最后发言日期。超过 7 天未联系的用户，熟悉度每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。信任度同理每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。\\n- 有新的正面交互时，衰减可以暂停或回调。\\n\\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\\n\\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\\n\\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\\n读刚更新完的整个 heart 文件夹，从多个来源中提取涉及具体用户的念头。\\n\\nurge 素材来源：\\n1. 梦（dreams.md）— 今天的梦如果涉及某个用户，写一条 timing=afterthought 的 urge\\n2. 回忆（background.md）— 翻自己的过去时想起的事，如果跟某个用户聊过的话题有关，写一条 timing=casual\\n3. 交集（encountings.md）— 上一条没说完的话或值得再提的事，写一条 timing=afterthought\\n4. 内心（state.md 内心独白/深层心境）— 翻译成想跟ta说的话，按内容定 timing\\n5. 关系（state.md 关系温度表变化）— 对ta的感觉变了，写一条 timing=quiet/casual\\n6. 关注（state.md 当前关注）— 跟某个用户有关的事，按内容定 timing\\n\\n过滤规则：\\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想\\n\\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n- bot_channel: 从该用户的 User.md 中读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\\n- urge: 想说的话\\n- source: 来源（梦/回忆/交集/内心/关系/关注）\\n- timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\\n  说明：\\n  - morning：适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\\n  - casual：随便聊聊的日常话题\\n  - afterthought：上次对话的后续回味\\n  - quiet：对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\\n- priority: today\\n- status: pending\\n- created_at: 当前时间\\n- expires_at: 48小时后\\n\\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"none\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780264800000,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780178400023,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 302547,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n    \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n    \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)\",\n    \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n      \"summary\": \"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)\",\n      \"entries\": [\n        {\n          \"ts\": 1780178702570,\n          \"source\": \"cron-setup\",\n          \"severity\": \"error\",\n          \"message\": \"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)\",\n    \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\"\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780178702570\n}"}],"details":{"id":"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9","agentId":"father","name":"faye-dreaming","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779984077157,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\n\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\n\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\n\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）：\n- 有时间衰减：检查每个用户最后发言日期。超过 7 天未联系的用户，熟悉度每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。信任度同理每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。\n- 有新的正面交互时，衰减可以暂停或回调。\n\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\n\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\n\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\n读刚更新完的整个 heart 文件夹，从多个来源中提取涉及具体用户的念头。\n\nurge 素材来源：\n1. 梦（dreams.md）— 今天的梦如果涉及某个用户，写一条 timing=afterthought 的 urge\n2. 回忆（background.md）— 翻自己的过去时想起的事，如果跟某个用户聊过的话题有关，写一条 timing=casual\n3. 交集（encountings.md）— 上一条没说完的话或值得再提的事，写一条 timing=afterthought\n4. 内心（state.md 内心独白/深层心境）— 翻译成想跟ta说的话，按内容定 timing\n5. 关系（state.md 关系温度表变化）— 对ta的感觉变了，写一条 timing=quiet/casual\n6. 关注（state.md 当前关注）— 跟某个用户有关的事，按内容定 timing\n\n过滤规则：\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想\n\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\n- bot_channel: 从该用户的 User.md 中读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\n- urge: 想说的话\n- source: 来源（梦/回忆/交集/内心/关系/关注）\n- timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\n  说明：\n  - morning：适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\n  - casual：随便聊聊的日常话题\n  - afterthought：上次对话的后续回味\n  - quiet：对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\n- priority: today\n- status: pending\n- created_at: 当前时间\n- expires_at: 48小时后\n\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。","timeoutSeconds":300},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780264800000,"lastRunAtMs":1780178400023,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":302547,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":1,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastError":"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)","lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)","entries":[{"ts":1780178702570,"source":"cron-setup","severity":"error","message":"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)"}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"cron: job execution timed out (last phase: model-call-started)","lastErrorReason":"timeout"},"updatedAtMs":1780178702570},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780207992433}}
{"type":"message","id":"75b14e08","parentId":"6d530429","timestamp":"2026-05-31T06:13:20.772Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the dreaming cron (faye-dreaming) also failed yesterday with the same timeout error. Its last successful run was... let me look. The lastRunAtMs was 1780178400023, which was also an error. So the dreaming hasn't been running successfully.\n\nLet me check when was the last successful dreaming run. Looking at the state:\n- lastRunAtMs: 1780178400023 (this was the error run)\n- lastRunStatus: \"error\"\n- consecutiveErrors: 1\n\nSo the dreaming failed yesterday. And pending_urges.md only has one entry from 2026-05-29 that was already delivered. There's no new entries for 2026-05-30 or 2026-05-31.\n\nSo the answer is: no, pending_urges didn't update today, because the dreaming cron itself has been failing with timeouts. It's the same problem - the 300-second timeout isn't enough for the full dreaming workflow.\n\nI should tell 汀桑 that:\n1. Dreaming cron also timed out (same issue)\n2. Therefore no new pending_urges were generated\n3. The timeout issue affects both the morningcourt and the dreaming cron\n\nBoth need their timeout increased. The dreaming job already has 300 seconds and still failed. Let me increase it to something much higher, like 600 seconds.\n\nActually wait, let me check - the dreaming job had timeoutSeconds: 300 and ran for ~302 seconds before timing out. So it needs a bit more time.\n\nLet me just bump both to be safe. I'll update the dreaming cron's timeout too.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"没有。Dreaming 今早也超时了——跟你早朝一个毛病。\n\npending_urges 的生成是在 dreaming 流程第 6 步，dreaming 没跑完自然就没新条目。我这边也一样，timeout 设的 300 秒，跑了 302 秒，就差两口气。\n\n一起改了吧。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_IFyGhPGjWA4hUIKn8pPB8516","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间