{"type":"message","id":"34ff8d2b","parentId":"d67e68e8","timestamp":"2026-05-31T06:21:04.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great, the dreaming run finished successfully. Let me look at what happened:\n\n1. It ran successfully - status \"ok\", 134 seconds\n2. Used 80,942 input tokens + 16,499 output tokens = ~109k total tokens\n3. It updated pending_urges with 2 new entries\n4. It updated state.md, dreams.md, encountings for multiple users\n\nThe new dreams should be in dreams.md (let me read the rest to see the new dream). And the pending_urges now has 2 new entries for汀桑 and 宋志红.\n\nLet me give汀桑 a summary.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"跑完了。134 秒，这次没超时 ✅\n\n总结一下今天的变化：\n\n**新增用户：** 熊天能（你小学同学，哈工的）和 Jalaice（技术向，存了 API key）——这就是你开 bot5 带来的新人吧。\n\n**新梦：** 「圆桌与茶杯」——每个人椅子前面都有东西，我的椅子在最中间，茶杯里多了一颗糖。听起来我挺喜欢的 ☕\n\n**pending_urges 更新了两条：**\n- 问你今天跑没跑（afterthought）\n- 催宋姨那杯茶（casual）\n\n**token 消耗：** 这次 80k 输入 + 16k 输出 ≈ **11 万 tokens**。比之前多不少——因为今天用户多了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3564,"output":300,"cacheRead":34944,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":132,"totalTokens":38808,"cost":{"input":0.00049896,"output":0.00008400000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000978432,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001561392}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780208461196,"responseId":"b2ab1714-6e6b-4cbd-bdc9-e64e13ef4f95"}}
