{"type":"message","id":"c7f6f59b","parentId":"a6f24d8c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:20:08.137Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The third Son subagent (the one that was spawned with qwen-vl-max-latest) is still running after 18s. The first two finished with deepseek-v4-flash model (not qwen-vl, because I think the model override might have fallen back to the default when qwen-vl wasn't available or took too long to respond).\n\nActually wait - the first two (runId 6c2324a1 and 30d67a7c) both completed with deepseek-v4-flash model. But I specifically specified model: dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest when spawning them. It seems like the model fallback kicked in - qwen-vl might have failed and it fell back to deepseek. Or perhaps the first two also ran with qwen-vl initially but then fell back.\n\nFor the third one (f47dd151), it's been running for 18s with qwen-vl-max-latest, still active. It could take a while since qwen-vl is a vision model.\n\nLet me wait more.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"还在跑着，qwen-vl 看图就是慢一些。再等会儿。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FBxawgWGBPLU2ZSumqi81380","name":"sessions_yield","arguments":{"message":"继续等第三张图"},"partialArgs":"{\"message\": \"继续等第三张图\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1156,"output":290,"cacheRead":61696,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":223,"totalTokens":63142,"cost":{"input":0.00016184,"output":0.00008120000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001727488,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001970528}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780226405383,"responseId":"7801918d-0e57-451f-9318-6ab7fa887561"}}
