{"type":"message","id":"add6dbe5","parentId":"22c5c064","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:20:18.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Son finished processing the third image. It seems like it just saved the image but didn't provide a detailed analysis of what's in it (perhaps because it fell back to deepseek which can't actually see images).\n\nThe output just says \"Image saved successfully\" and gave an album ID. It didn't describe what's in the image.\n\nGiven the context - 汀桑之前发了华侨城的夜景照片，这是第三张，应该也是他昨晚在华侨城拍的夜景。但既然 Son 没有给出图片内容的描述，我只能根据之前照片的类型推测了。\n\n汀桑问\"讲的是啥啊\" - 他在问图片里是什么。\n\n看来 qwen-vl 模型还是有access denied的问题，Son 也 fallback 到 deepseek 了，deepseek不能看图所以只存了照片。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"第三张也存上了，但你那 qwen-vl 模型抽风一直报 403，Son 直接 fallback 到普通模型了——能存不能看😓\n\n前两张我知道是昨晚华侨城的夜景，第三张也是那会儿拍的？你要是自己记得传的啥就告诉我是啥，我标注一下。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4872,"output":236,"cacheRead":58240,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":165,"totalTokens":63348,"cost":{"input":0.0006820800000000001,"output":0.00006608,"cacheRead":0.00163072,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00237888}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780226415020,"responseId":"e94c656a-4b00-462e-8ea6-e42931440414"}}
