{"type":"message","id":"1afd963f","parentId":"5afeb230","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:21:55.489Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same key! \"sk-ff3...e82b\" matches. So the key is already configured but qwen-vl was returning 403. \n\nPossible reasons:\n1. This key might not have access to the qwen-vl-max-latest model - it could be a key that only has access to certain models\n2. The key might need the model to be activated/authorized in the Alibaba Cloud console\n3. The key could have insufficient quota\n\nLet me tell 汀桑 the key is already there but the model call was still failing with 403.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已经在了。现在配的这个就是 `sk-ff3e…e82b`——前六后四都对得上。\n\n但模型还是报了 403。所以不是没配的问题，是这个 key 可能没开 qwen-vl-max-latest 的权限，或者额度用完了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":151,"output":181,"cacheRead":63616,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":119,"totalTokens":63948,"cost":{"input":0.00002114,"output":0.00005068,"cacheRead":0.001781248,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001853068}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780226513052,"responseId":"81c66bc0-4879-458c-ae58-2677d2bdbbbf"}}
