{"type":"message","id":"a2bd880e","parentId":"62343b65","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:37:41.153Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, interesting. The qwen3-vl-flash model returned an error saying \"Output data may contain inappropriate content\" - the safety/content moderation system flagged the output as potentially inappropriate.\n\nThis is probably just the safety moderation on the output side being too aggressive. But the image itself seems to trigger the content moderation. Let me look at the image directly.\n\nWait, let me check - the original file was 863x1920, 120KB, JPEG. Let me see if I can open it or get any info about it.\n\nActually, let me try the original qwen-vl-max-latest model which was working before.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5mNcBMWMYZ1XReoJhkaY3452","name":"image","arguments":{"model":"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest","image":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/tmp_view.jpg","prompt":"请详细描述这张照片的所有可见内容，包括场景、物体、文字等任何细节"},"partialArgs":"{\"model\": \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\", \"image\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/tmp_view.jpg\", \"prompt\": \"请详细描述这张照片的所有可见内容，包括场景、物体、文字等任何细节\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":146,"output":246,"cacheRead":70912,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":130,"totalTokens":71304,"cost":{"input":0.00002044,"output":0.00006888,"cacheRead":0.001985536,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002074856}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780227458767,"responseId":"dae3da86-8886-432f-8ea6-aa83f4dfde7e"}}
