{"type":"message","id":"0af41794","parentId":"6204f18b","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:45:56.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说用\"Wan2.7-Image-Pro\"作为生图模型。这是阿里云百炼（通义万相）的文生图模型。\n\n让我查一下这个模型的具体信息。Wan2.7-Image-Pro 应该是通义万相系列的一个文生图模型。\n\n我需要：\n1. 先看看这个模型在 dashscope 上怎么调用\n2. 配置到 openclaw.json 的 dashscope provider 里\n3. 创建生图功能的 function.md\n4. 注册到 trigger_prompt.md\n\n不过汀桑说\"先配置到son的skill里面\" - 他可能是指直接在 Son 的配置里加一个 skill 或者功能定义，还不是完整走注册流程。\n\n让我先查一下这个模型的信息，看看怎么配置。\n\n实际上，这应该是一个通过 API 调用的文生图模型。阿里云百炼的 Wan2.7 系列应该有对应的 API。\n\n让我看看 Son 那边有没有 skills 目录或者类似的结构，再看看怎么配置。\n\n汀桑说\"先配置到son的skill里面\" - 可能是指在 Son 的 skills 目录下加一个 skill 定义文件，这样 Son 就可以调用这个模型来生图。\n\n让我先看看 Son 的 workspace 结构。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9MfevIUOiZ9eyDsitYHk5838","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/skills/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"no skills dir\"\necho \"---\"\nls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/ 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/skills/ 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"no skills dir\\\"\\necho \\\"---\\\"\\nls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/ 2>/dev/null\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_c8oVSD0ysY5E3ecvMyrG6182","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | grep -A 30 '\"dashscope\"'"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | grep -A 30 '\\\"dashscope\\\"'\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2103,"output":411,"cacheRead":73728,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":266,"totalTokens":76242,"cost":{"input":0.00029442000000000004,"output":0.00011508,"cacheRead":0.002064384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002473884}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780227952968,"responseId":"9797714f-ed1f-47ab-b047-280c9c979782"}}
