{"type":"message","id":"5cdb2a36","parentId":"afa95b07","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:46:19.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The docs URL returned 404. Let me try the OpenAI-compatible image generation API endpoint. Based on my knowledge, Dashscope supports the OpenAI-compatible API for image generation at:\n\nPOST https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1/images/generations\n\nWith request body:\n```json\n{\n  \"model\": \"wan2.7-image-pro\",\n  \"prompt\": \"your prompt here\",\n  \"n\": 1,\n  \"size\": \"1024x1024\"\n}\n```\n\nThis should work with the same API key. But the issue is that openclaw.json configures the dashscope provider with `\"api\": \"openai-completions\"` which means the models are expected to be text completion models, not image generation.\n\nFor image generation, I'd need to add the model to the dashscope provider, but with a different API type or at least acknowledge that it uses a different endpoint.\n\nActually, let me take a practical approach. Let me just test the API first to see if it works.\n\nActually, 汀桑 said \"先配置到son的skill里面\" - so he wants me to create a skill/function for image generation in Son's workspace, and handle the API call within the skill logic. Son would use curl to call the API directly, not through OpenClaw's model routing.\n\nLet me create the function definition for Son's image generation capability.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了，wan2.7-image-pro 在阿里云百炼的\"图像生成\"分类下。我先测试一下能不能直接调通。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_3CZUZwvXa7w1PS41TfLf9931","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1/images/generations\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-ff3…e82b\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"wan2.7-image-pro\",\n    \"prompt\": \"a cute cat sitting on a desk, digital art style\",\n    \"n\": 1,\n    \"size\": \"1024x1024\"\n  }' 2>&1 | head -30","timeout":30},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"curl -s -X POST \\\"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1/images/generations\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer sk-ff3…e82b\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\n    \\\"model\\\": \\\"wan2.7-image-pro\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"a cute cat sitting on a desk, digital art style\\\",\\n    \\\"n\\\": 1,\\n    \\\"size\\\": \\\"1024x1024\\\"\\n  }' 2>&1 | head -30\", \"timeout\": 30}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2473,"output":516,"cacheRead":84608,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":294,"totalTokens":87597,"cost":{"input":0.00034622,"output":0.00014448,"cacheRead":0.002369024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002859724}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780227975031,"responseId":"f647b4e5-b172-4617-b1e2-351a22548fbb"}}
