{"type":"message","id":"b716f89e","parentId":"01347173","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:46:52.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All the help.alibabacloud.com URLs are returning 404 or empty pages when fetched via web_fetch. They're probably JS-rendered SPAs.\n\nLet me try to find the correct API format by looking at known Dashscope API patterns. The Dashscope text-to-image API typically uses a task-based system.\n\nThe correct endpoint should be:\n`POST https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/text2image/image-synthesis`\n\nWith the body format:\n```json\n{\n  \"model\": \"wan2.7-image-pro\",\n  \"input\": {\n    \"prompt\": \"text description\"\n  },\n  \"parameters\": {\n    \"size\": \"1024x1024\",\n    \"n\": 1\n  }\n}\n```\n\nBut earlier I got \"task can not be null\" from the `/api/v1/services/text2image/image-synthesis` endpoint without `aigc/` prefix. And \"url error\" from `aigc/text2image/text2image`. Let me try the correct one.\n\nActually, let me try to find the correct API by looking at the available APIs!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_R9GOAP4LCqaQJguQQcgY0712","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 15 -X POST \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/text2image/image-synthesis\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-ff3…e82b\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"wan2.7-image-pro\",\n    \"input\": {\n      \"prompt\": \"a cute orange cat sitting on a desk\"\n    },\n    \"parameters\": {\n      \"size\": \"1024x1024\",\n      \"n\": 1\n    }\n  }' 2>&1","timeout":20},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"curl -s --max-time 15 -X POST \\\"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/text2image/image-synthesis\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer sk-ff3…e82b\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\n    \\\"model\\\": \\\"wan2.7-image-pro\\\",\\n    \\\"input\\\