{"type":"message","id":"7fe0ccb4","parentId":"c2180519","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:47:26.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see. The providers are configured with `\"api\": \"openai-completions\"` which means they use the OpenAI-compatible chat completions format. For image generation, I'd need a different approach.\n\nLet me take a practical approach. I'll:\n1. Create the image generation function for Son that uses `curl` to call the dashscope API directly\n2. Son will handle the async task submission and polling\n\nBut first, let me figure out the correct API format. Let me try the older Wanx API format.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_25SQfgKkkWTm7FOWgngS4692","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try the Wanx v1.0 API format\ncurl -s --max-time 30 -X POST \\\n  \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/text2image/text-to-image\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-ff3…e82b\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"wan2.7-image-pro\",\n    \"input\": {\n      \"text\": \"a cute orange cat on a desk\"\n    },\n    \"parameters\": {\n      \"size\": \"1024x1024\",\n      \"n\": 1\n    }\n  }' 2>&1","timeout":35},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Try the Wanx v1.0 API format\\ncurl -s --max-time 30 -X POST \\\\\\n  \\\"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/text2image/text-to-image\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer sk-ff3…e82b\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\n    \\\"model\\\": \\\"wan2.7-image-pro\\\",\\n    \\\"input\\\": {\\n      \\\"text\\\": \\\"a cute orange cat on a desk\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"parameters\\\": {\\n      \\\"size\\\": \\\"1024x1024\\\",\\n      \\\"n\\\": 1\\n    }\\n  }' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 35}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":209,"output":331,"cacheRead":99200,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningT