{"type":"message","id":"004809c1","parentId":"5f9350a6","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:48:35.338Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The image generation succeeded! I got:\n- task_status: SUCCEEDED\n- An image URL: https://dashscope-7c2c.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/1d/94/20260531/218dd9c9/30d42971-64b1-4349-8e92-bb3588f46f87_0.png?Expires=...\n- Usage: 1864 input tokens, 2 output tokens, 1 image, total 1866 tokens\n\nSo the API works! Now I need to:\n1. Download this image to show 汀桑\n2. Create the function definition for Son to handle image generation\n3. Configure everything properly\n\nLet me first download the image to show 汀桑 it works.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"生图成功了！拿下看看效果。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ROZejCqt1kAr5gihBuCv1462","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -L --max-time 30 \\\n  \"https://dashscope-7c2c.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/1d/94/20260531/218dd9c9/30d42971-64b1-4349-8e92-bb3588f46f87_0.png?Expires=1780314507&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5t…rym1&Signature=qc8B8D…M%3D\" \\\n  -o /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/tmp_gen_image.png 2>&1 && echo \"done\" && ls -lh /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/tmp_gen_image.png","timeout":35},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"curl -s -L --max-time 30 \\\\\\n  \\\"https://dashscope-7c2c.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/1d/94/20260531/218dd9c9/30d42971-64b1-4349-8e92-bb3588f46f87_0.png?Expires=1780314507&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5t…rym1&Signature=qc8B8D…%3D\\\" \\\\\\n  -o /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/tmp_gen_image.png 2>&1 && echo \\\"done\\\" && ls -lh /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/tmp_gen_image.png\", \"timeout\": 35}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":338,"output":427,"cacheRead":103424,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":169,"totalTokens":104189,"cost":{"input":0.00004732,"output":0.00011956000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002895872,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0030627519999999997}},"stopReason