{"type":"message","id":"281f9d17","parentId":"be490494","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:48:38.670Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me show this to 汀桑 using MEDIA directive.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"API 通了。你给的 key 能生图，但走的是异步任务模式——提交→等→拿结果。你看：\n\nMEDIA:/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/tmp_gen_image.png\n\nAPI 参数也摸清了：\n- 端点：`POST /api/v1/services/aigc/image-generation/generation`\n- 格式：`input.messages` + `role: user, content: [{type: text, text: \"prompt\"}]`\n- 大小用 `1024*1024` 这种\n- 异步：加 header `X-DashScope-Async: enable`\n- 轮询：`GET /api/v1/tasks/{task_id}` 等 SUCCEEDED\n\n现在开始配 Son 那边的功能定义？触发词想好了吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":177,"output":187,"cacheRead":104064,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":13,"totalTokens":104428,"cost":{"input":0.000024780000000000003,"output":0.00005236000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002913792,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002990932}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780228116244,"responseId":"fa9046f8-9a7e-4592-8ac3-bf81fadb56eb"}}
