{"type":"message","id":"7c556d98","parentId":"45aee671","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:51:26.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑确认了。那我需要执行注册流程的 Step 4：\n\n1. 确认 Spirit 标记 ✅（把 ⏳ 改成 ✅）\n2. 更新 trigger_prompt.md（我自己写）\n3. 同步功能定义到 Son（通知 Spirit 复制文件 + 更新 manifest）\n4. 通知 Son 建数据目录\n\n让我先确认 Spirit 那边已经在 bot_function_explain.md 里加了条目但用的是 ⏳ 状态。然后依次执行。\n\n实际上我先把这几步都做了。\n\nStep 1: 确认 Spirit 标记\nStep 2: 我自己更新 trigger_prompt.md\nStep 3: 让 Spirit 更新标记 + 复制文件到 Son\nStep 4: 让 Son 建目录\n\n我应该先更新 trigger_prompt.md（我自己做），然后同时让 Spirit 改标记+同步文件，让 Son 建目录。\n\n先读一下 trigger_prompt.md 看看当前内容，然后在表格末尾追加新行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_K6HJYnOyPYNw7qlhqjPs2692","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md","offset":35,"limit":10},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\", \"offset\": 35, \"limit\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2513,"output":296,"cacheRead":103680,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":206,"totalTokens":106489,"cost":{"input":0.00035182000000000003,"output":0.00008288,"cacheRead":0.00290304,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00333774}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780228283668,"responseId":"d9469d41-bd58-4b27-aff1-ad48894eb4a6"}}
