{"type":"message","id":"845afb3e","parentId":"cf49d4b9","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:58:16.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑问音乐生成模型推荐什么。之前在阿里云百炼的模型列表里看到过 \"fun-music-v1\" 这个音乐生成模型。让我查查还有什么选择。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"记得百炼模型列表里有 `fun-music-v1`，不过让我看看还有啥。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ICjOasHYIhzxYL02tWbY1258","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 先看看之前那个key能不能调音乐生成\ncurl -s --max-time 15 \\\n  \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/music-generation/generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer ***…e82b\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"X-DashScope-Async: enable\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\": \"fun-music-v1\", \"input\": {\"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"test\"}]}]}}' 2>&1","timeout":20},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# 先看看之前那个key能不能调音乐生成\\ncurl -s --max-time 15 \\\\\\n  \\\"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/music-generation/generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer ***…e82b\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"X-DashScope-Async: enable\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\\"model\\\": \\\"fun-music-v1\\\", \\\"input\\\": {\\\"messages\\\": [{\\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\", \\\"content\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"text\\\": \\\"test\\\"}]}]}}' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 20}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3807,"output":259,"cacheRead":105856,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":39,"totalTokens":109922,"cost":{"input":0.0005329800000000001,"output":0.00007252,"cacheRead":0.002963968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003569468}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780228693645,"responseId":"6f9e29c7-4b8e-436e-8ce2-b665316d5827"}}
