{"type":"message","id":"a1da333d","parentId":"b60cb569","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:58:50.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说先把音乐生成配到 Son 的 skill 里，先不注册功能，先配置。\n\n我需要在 Son 那边加一个音乐生成的功能定义（类似于 draw），然后在 trigger_prompt 里加触发词。\n\n不过汀桑说\"先配置son\" - 意思可能是直接在 Son 那边能调用就行，先不管触发词之类的。\n\n但我觉得他意思是：先把音乐生成的 API 调用能力配到 Son 里，让 Son 能调用这个 API 生音乐。\n\n跟画图一样，我直接做：\n1. 创建 music/song 生成功能定义放到 Son 的 functions/ 下\n2. 更新 functions_manifest.md\n\n或者更简单——直接在 Son 的 AGENTS.md 或 TOOLS.md 里记录这个 API 的能力，让 Son 知道怎么调。\n\n不过按照之前画图的模式，最好还是创建一个 function.md 文件放在 Son 的 functions/ 目录下，然后更新 manifest。\n\n让我先测试一下这个 API 能不能用当前的 key 调通。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"先试试 key 能不能调通这个 API。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_DHbI0ViLNZE4DhpXE9bu6228","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 30 -X POST \\\n  \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/audio/music/generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer ***…e82b\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"fun-music-v1\",\n    \"input\": {\n      \"prompt\": \"轻快的吉他旋律，适合午后的阳光，轻松愉悦，长度30秒\",\n      \"gender\": \"female\"\n    }\n  }' 2>&1","timeout":35},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"curl -s --max-time 30 -X POST \\\\\\n  \\\"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/audio/music/generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer ***…e82b\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\n    \\\"model\\\": \\\"fun-music-v1\\\",\\n    \\\"input\\\": {\\n      \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"轻快的吉他旋律，适合午后的阳光，轻松愉悦，长度30秒\\\",\\n      \\\"gender\\\": \\\"female\\\"\\n    }\\n  }' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 35}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4025,"output":410,"cacheRead":108544,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":216,"totalTokens":112979,"cost":{"input":0.0005635000000000001,"output":0.00011480000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003039232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003717532}}