{"type":"message","id":"04a5a265","parentId":"1975c23e","timestamp":"2026-05-31T11:58:54.279Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\"Invalid API-key provided\" - so the same API key doesn't work for the music generation service. It likely needs a different API key or a different authorization for this specific service.\n\nLet me check if there's a different API key for the music service, or if it needs to be enabled separately.\n\nActually, looking at the error more carefully - \"InvalidApiKey\" not \"InvalidParameter\" or \"AccessDenied\". This means the API key itself is not valid for this particular service endpoint. It might use a different authentication mechanism or a different API key entirely.\n\nIt's possible that the fun-music service requires a separate API key or has its own billing setup.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这个 key 对音乐生成不通用——报的 InvalidApiKey，不是额度/权限问题。音乐生成可能要单独的 key 或者另外开通。\n\n你现在用的这个 key（sk-ff3…e82b）能跑图、能跑文字，但音乐那边没授权。你要是有另一个音乐专用的 key 给我配上，或者你在百炼控制台看看 fun-music-v1 开通了没。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":135,"output":223,"cacheRead":112896,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":136,"totalTokens":113254,"cost":{"input":0.000018900000000000002,"output":0.00006244,"cacheRead":0.003161088,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003242428}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780228731426,"responseId":"4b52f6a0-0fd3-420b-b08c-4c7be94558b1"}}
