{"type":"message","id":"aaedf8fd","parentId":"c0d059f0","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:10:20.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Son processed the image but just saved it to album without description again. 汀桑 asked \"这个什么意思\" - he probably means he wants to know what the image is, not just \"saved successfully\". \n\nBut wait - the image might be the MiniMax music generation pricing page or something from his earlier question about music models. Let me describe it properly this time. The Son's album \"view\" action just saves the image, it doesn't describe it. I need Son to actually analyze it.\n\nLet me spawn Son again with a \"describe\" or analysis action.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你又没给我描述——Son 那家伙只会存不会看。让我正经看看这张图。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Ixb5HlQoeDkW3V0w9cRx8557","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/24D28E7FDA618AB4F6C498B6C2A719F4_1780229365435_dd7109.jpg /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/tmp_look.jpg"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cp /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/24D28E7FDA618AB4F6C498B6C2A719F4_1780229365435_dd7109.jpg /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/tmp_look.jpg\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":12016,"output":239,"cacheRead":104192,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":116,"totalTokens":116447,"cost":{"input":0.0016822400000000002,"output":0.00006692,"cacheRead":0.0029173759999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004666536}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780229416625,"responseId":"6306fe9c-6f73-4e9d-9a9e-3d8b76d871e8"}}
