{"type":"message","id":"0897857e","parentId":"97db6152","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:11:24.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Search is still broken. But based on what the image showed:\n- \"即日起，MiniMax Music 2.6 全球创作内测开启，14 天限免\"\n- C端用户：每账号每日 500 首免费创作额度\n- 开发者：现 Token Plan 用户额外获赠 100 首/天免费调用额度\n\nSo the info on the image says \"14天限免\" for the internal testing period. The \"500首/天\" seems like a general free tier. \n\nThe image said \"14 天限免\" and \"即日起\" (effective from now). So it started now (end of May 2026) and lasts 14 days.\n\nAs for whether it needs an invitation code or just login - the image doesn't mention invitation codes, just \"C端产品体验\" which suggests you just go to the site and use it. The \"14天限免\" might be the special promotion period, but the \"500首/天\" could be the ongoing free tier.\n\nLet me just tell 汀桑 what I can see from the image.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"图上写的就这些信息：\n\n- **即日起**开启全球创作内测\n- **14 天限免**\n- **C端用户：** 每账号每天 500 首免费额度（不像要邀请码，登录即送）\n- **开发者：** 现有 Token Plan 用户额外 +100 首/天\n\n没有提到需要邀请码之类的门槛，应该就是登录就能用。持续时间图里写的 **14 天**，从\"即日起\"算——就是这波推广限免的意思。\n\n入口：`minimaxi.com/audio/music`\nAPI：`platform.minimaxi.com/docs/api-reference/music-generation`\n\n要不要我去申请个 MiniMax 的 API key 配到 Son 里？跟画图一样走异步提交→轮询拿结果。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":77,"output":399,"cacheRead":118144,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":231,"totalTokens":118620,"cost":{"input":0.00001078,"output":0.00011172000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003308032,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003430532}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780229480003,"responseId":"d8ad2688-78cf-4948-8ce0-9ea012f19485"}}
