{"type":"message","id":"0c8c044d","parentId":"4190c03e","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:17:55.768Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑发了一个 MiniMax 的 API key。看起来是 `***...` 开头的 key。他这是注册好了 MiniMax 然后给了 key，让我配上去。\n\n现在我需要把这个 key 配置到 OpenClaw 里，让 Son 可以调用 MiniMax 的 API 来生成音乐。\n\nMiniMax 的 API 信息：\n- Endpoint: `https://api.minimaxi.com`\n- API: `/v1/music_generation`\n- Models: music-2.6, music-2.6-free, music-cover, music-cover-free\n\n我需要：\n1. 把 MiniMax 的 key 加到环境变量或者 openclaw.json 里\n2. 配置 MiniMax 作为一个 provider\n\n让我先看看 openclaw.json 里的 providers 结构，然后加一个新的 MiniMax provider。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，MiniMax 的 key 拿到了。配进去。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vw2RMxeLjP5KweAwo8fS3340","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | grep -A5 '\"providers\"' | head -10"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | grep -A5 '\\\"providers\\\"' | head -10\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3762,"output":257,"cacheRead":118400,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":180,"totalTokens":122419,"cost":{"input":0.0005266800000000001,"output":0.00007196000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0033152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00391384}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780229872286,"responseId":"8929190c-3f27-492f-ab84-49907f3d48b9"}}
