{"type":"message","id":"815efd0d","parentId":"3c403877","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:18:32.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\"insufficient balance\" - the key works but the balance is insufficient. `music-2.6-free` should be the free version, but it seems like even the free version requires some balance or the account hasn't been set up properly yet.\n\nWait - the API docs said `music-2.6-free` is available for \"所有用户可通过 API Key 使用\". But it returned \"insufficient balance\". \n\nMaybe 汀桑 just registered and hasn't topped up the balance yet. Or maybe the free tier also requires at least some balance to start using.\n\nLet me tell 汀桑 the key works but it says \"insufficient balance\".","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Key 能通，请求发出去了，但返回 **\"insufficient balance\"**（余额不足）。\n\n`music-2.6-free` 虽然是限免版本，但看起来还是得账户里有余额才能调。你**刚注册 MiniMax，还没充值**对吧？哪怕有免费额度，可能也得先充个最低金额激活账户才能用。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":114,"output":209,"cacheRead":124672,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":133,"totalTokens":124995,"cost":{"input":0.00001596,"output":0.00005852,"cacheRead":0.003490816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003565296}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780229909726,"responseId":"e1e12859-14b4-4ef4-a9cf-6dca4b85629a"}}
