{"type":"message","id":"1bf49328","parentId":"179c316a","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:18:56.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All set. Now I should also update Father's AGENTS.md model routing table to include the new model alias for minimax. Actually minimax is not a model provider in openclaw, so it doesn't need an alias. The API key is stored in Son's .env.\n\nLet me summarize what I did for汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配好了。梳理一下：\n\n**已做：**\n- ✅ Son 的 `functions/music_function.md` — 功能定义（API 地址、参数、格式都写好了）\n- ✅ `functions_manifest.md` — 追加了 `music` 行\n- ✅ Son 的 `music/` 数据目录已建\n- ✅ `trigger_prompt.md` — 加了 `/音乐` `/翻唱` 触发词\n- ✅ MiniMax key 存到 Son 的环境变量里了\n\n**触发词：**\n- `/音乐 轻快的夏日民谣`\n- `/音乐 悲伤的钢琴曲 --纯音乐`\n- `/音乐 流行情歌 --歌词 你的歌词`\n- `/翻唱 参考音频URL --风格 摇滚`\n\n不过你现在 MiniMax 账户还报 **insufficient balance**，得先充点进去才能用。去 `platform.minimaxi.com` 看看充值入口？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":68,"output":266,"cacheRead":126720,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":68,"totalTokens":127054,"cost":{"input":0.00000952,"output":0.00007448,"cacheRead":0.00354816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0036321599999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780229932659,"responseId":"7165ccc8-b72c-4d5d-807e-29ba26c69094"}}
