{"type":"message","id":"9d3c4928","parentId":"9e9d235a","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:23:01.597Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑问了两件事：\n1. 他充值了 MiniMax，现在能不能调通音乐生成\n2. QQ 能不能发音频文件或语音\n\n第二个问题我可以直接回答——QQ Bot 发送音频文件是可以的，但语音消息可能有限制。QQ Bot 支持发送文件（包括音频文件 mp3/wav 等），但语音消息（语音通话那种）需要特定的语音消息接口。\n\n第一个问题——我需要试试现在 MiniMax 的 API 能不能调通，因为他充值了。\n\n让我先试试 API。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xuUZkJpvCUvdIakuV85C6702","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 40 -X POST \\\n  \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer ***…xIA0\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"music-2.6-free\",\n    \"prompt\": \"轻快的吉他旋律，夏日午后，放松心情\",\n    \"lyrics\": \"阳光洒在窗台\\n微风轻轻吹来\\n这一刻的时光\\n刚好用来发呆\",\n    \"lyrics_optimizer\": false,\n    \"is_instrumental\": false,\n    \"output_format\": \"url\"\n  }' 2>&1","timeout":60},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"curl -s --max-time 40 -X POST \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer ***…xIA0\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\n    \\\"model\\\": \\\"music-2.6-free\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"轻快的吉他旋律，夏日午后，放松心情\\\",\\n    \\\"lyrics\\\": \\\"阳光洒在窗台\\\\n微风轻轻吹来\\\\n这一刻的时光\\\\n刚好用来发呆\\\",\\n    \\\"lyrics_optimizer\\\": false,\\n    \\\"is_instrumental\\\": false,\\n    \\\"output_format\\\": \\\"url\\\"\\n  }' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 60}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5343,"output":319,"cacheRead":121728,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":111,"totalTokens":127390,"cost":{"input":0.0007480200000000001,"output":0.00008932,"cacheRead":0.003408384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004245724}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780230177764,"responseId":"0cc01e99-8f06-4263-b442-bf5b8d80e386"}}
