{"type":"message","id":"7ebc92ab","parentId":"234c4713","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:24:14.804Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_PmVuJIRsm7SrFGzM45Sf8044","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"data\":null,\"trace_id\":\"066b5b3ee18707f7ef77dc3a46df75ce\",\"extra_info\":null,\"analysis_info\":null,\"base_resp\":{\"status_code\":1008,\"status_msg\":\"insufficient balance\"}}\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"warm-summit","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"{\"data\":null,\"trace_id\":\"066b5b3ee18707f7ef77dc3a46df75ce\",\"extra_info\":null,\"analysis_info\":null,\"base_resp\":{\"status_code\":1008,\"status_msg\":\"insufficient balance\"}}","name":"curl 120"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780230254803}}
{"type":"message","id":"6de6c67c","parentId":"7ebc92ab","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:24:18.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still \"insufficient balance\". So 汀桑 hasn't actually charged yet, or his recharge hasn't taken effect yet.\n\nLet me now answer his question about whether QQ can send audio files. The QQ Bot (OpenClaw's QQ channel) should be able to send audio files - I know it can send images via MEDIA: tag. For audio, the medium might be different.\n\nLet me check the qqbot-media skill since it mentions \"voice\" and \"file\" attachments.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"还是 `insufficient balance`——充值可能还没生效，或者充的不够游戏门槛。\n\n至于 QQ 发音频——QQ Bot 支持 **发文件**，音频文件（mp3/wav）能当文件发出去。但**语音消息**（像微信那种按住说话的语音气泡）不一定支持，得看你用的这个 QQ Bot 通道。\n\n看看这 skill 怎么说："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Fm34a3CissjxvL50lJQs4323","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":74,"output":241,"cacheRead":129792,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":100,"totalTokens":130107,"cost":{"input":0.00001036,"output":0.00006748000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003634176,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003712016}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780230254826,"responseId":"3467347d-2224-470a-9d01-8e500f90cc82"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f19caf30","parentId":"6de6c67c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:24:18.623Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Fm34a3CissjxvL50lJQs4323","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md'"},"isError":true,"timestamp":1780230258622}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad39bf11","parentId":"f19caf30","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:24:20.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The path in the available skills list was `~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md` - let me check there.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_XKHycFqa63FWqRYSmW9P0963","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/plugin-skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/plugin-skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":124,"output":93,"cacheRead":130048,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":33,"totalTokens":130265,"cost":{"input":0.00001736,"output":0.00002604,"cacheRead":0.003641344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0036847439999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780230258642,"responseId":"36cd4933-f2e7-4ba4-8af7-435455c79db3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd250479","parentId":"ad39bf11","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:24:20.809Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_XKHycFqa63FWqRYSmW9P0963","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: qqbot-media\ndescription: QQBot rich media send and receive support. Use <qqmedia> tags to send image, voice, video, or file attachments, with the media type inferred from the file extension.\nmetadata: { \"openclaw\": { \"emoji\": \"📸\", \"requires\": { \"config\": [\"channels.qqbot\"] } } }\n---\n\n# QQBot 富媒体收发\n\n## 用法\n\n```\n<qqmedia>路径或URL</qqmedia>\n```\n\n系统根据文件扩展名自动识别类型并路由：\n\n- `.jpg/.png/.gif/.webp/.bmp` → 图片\n- `.silk/.wav/.mp3/.ogg/.aac/.flac` 等 → 语音\n- `.mp4/.mov/.avi/.mkv/.webm` 等 → 视频\n- 其他扩展名 → 文件\n- 无扩展名的 URL → 默认按图片处理\n\n## 接收媒体\n\n- 用户发来的**图片**自动下载到本地，路径在上下文【附件】中，可直接用 `<qqmedia>路径</qqmedia>` 回发\n- 用户发来的**语音**路径在上下文中；若有 STT 能力则优先转写\n\n## 规则\n\n1. **路径必须是绝对路径**（以 `/` 或 `http` 开头）\n2. **标签必须用开闭标签包裹路径**：`<qqmedia>路径</qqmedia>`\n3. **待发送的本地文件须落在 OpenClaw 媒体目录下**：生成、下载或复制出的文件应写入 **`~/.openclaw/media/qqbot/`**（或其子目录），再写进 `<qqmedia>`。不要只放在 `~/.openclaw/workspace/` 等工作区根目录——平台安全策略只允许从 `~/.openclaw/media/`（含 `media/qqbot`）等受信根路径上传，否则会拦截、发不出去。\n4. **文件大小上限**：图片 30MB / 视频 100MB / 文件 100MB / 语音 20MB\n5. **你有能力发送本地图片/文件**，直接用标签包裹路径即可，**不要说\"无法发送\"**\n6. 发送语音时不要重复语音中已朗读的文字\n7. 多个媒体用多个标签\n8. 以会话上下文中的能力说明为准（如未启用语音则不要发语音）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780230260809}}
{"type":"message","id":"4198717f","parentId":"fd250479","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:24:23.193Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So I can use `<qqmedia>路径</qqmedia>` to send audio files. The supported audio formats are `.silk/.wav/.mp3/.ogg/.aac/.flac`. \n\nAs long as the audio file is in `~/.openclaw/media/qqbot/` directory, it can be sent.\n\nLet me answer 汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"关于 QQ 发音频，可以。`<qqmedia>` 标签支持发 mp3/wav/flac 等格式的音频文件，上限 20MB。\n\n但现在关键问题是——你 MiniMax **余额还是不够**啊😅 刚才试了还是 `insufficient balance`。你充了多少？可能得等一会儿才生效，或者得去 `platform.minimaxi.com` 确认一下余额到账了没。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":631,"output":168,"cacheRead":130176,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":76,"totalTokens":130975,"cost":{"input":0.00008834000000000001,"output":0.000047040000000000004,"cacheRead":0.003644928,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003780308}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780230260829,"responseId":"b6e9a75d-da80-4ca1-90c2-0429e5d09326"}}
