{"type":"message","id":"ea1e2f02","parentId":"6ab53dee","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:29:37.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both keys have issues:\n1. First key (sk-ff3...e82b) → insufficient balance\n2. Second key (sk-cp-Xr...lVY) → token plan doesn't support music-2.6-free, and music-2.6 times out\n\n汀桑 might need to configure his token plan correctly on the MiniMax platform to enable the music generation model. Let me tell him.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这 key 能用，但问题不太一样——之前那个余额不足，这个是不支持 `music-2.6-free` 模型，而 `music-2.6`（付费版）请求发过去了但 MiniMax 那边一直不返回。\n\n你需要去 MiniMax 平台确认两件事：\n1. **Token Plan 有没有勾选 Music 模型的权限**——可能在控制台里要手动开通\n2. **这个 key 是 API 密钥还是 Token Plan 的 Token**——MiniMax 有两种认证方式，API key 和 Token Plan 可能不是同一个"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":53,"output":209,"cacheRead":133120,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":87,"totalTokens":133382,"cost":{"input":0.00000742,"output":0.00005852,"cacheRead":0.00372736,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037933}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780230574248,"responseId":"ea8a4fa2-4522-4fb8-ae57-49ca898d956e"}}
