{"type":"message","id":"ea49928e","parentId":"5bec37a2","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:31:07.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说他是买的积分，不是订阅 Token Plan。所以之前那个 `sk-cp-…0lVY` key 是积分制的 API key，不是 Token Plan 订阅用户。\n\n那 `music-2.6-free` 报 \"your current token plan not support\" 可能是个误导——他用的是积分 key，可能直接调 `music-2.6` 付费版就能扣积分跑，但之前 `music-2.6` 请求超时了。\n\n让我换个思路——直接试 `music-2.6` 付费模型，用积分扣费模式再试一次。可能之前超时是因为 MiniMax 服务器处理时间很长。\n\n或者，MiniMax 对积分用户可能需要传不同的参数或者模型名。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"积分用户！那之前报 \"token plan not support music-2.6-free\" 就说得通了——你根本没 Token Plan，所以 free 模型不让你调。\n\n直接试 `music-2.6` 付费版，积分扣费跑一次看看。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_0IyBxFMnoSxlpf46jHqH9492","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try music-2.6 paid model with credits, wait up to 3 minutes\ncurl -s --max-time 180 -X POST \\\n  \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer ***…0lVY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"music-2.6\",\n    \"prompt\": \"轻快的吉他旋律，夏日午后，轻松愉快的氛围\",\n    \"lyrics_optimizer\": true,\n    \"is_instrumental\": true,\n    \"output_format\": \"url\"\n  }' 2>&1","timeout":185},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Try music-2.6 paid model with credits, wait up to 3 minutes\\ncurl -s --max-time 180 -X POST \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer ***…0lVY\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\n    \\\"model\\\": \\\"music-2.6\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"轻快的吉他旋律，夏日午后，轻松愉快的氛围\\\",\\n    \\\"lyrics_optimizer\\\": true,\\n    \\\"is_instrumental\\\": true,\\n    \\\"output_format\\\": \\\"url\\\"\\n  }' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 185}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2497,"output":418,"cacheRead":131072,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":158,"totalTokens":133987,"cost":{"input":0.00034958,"out