{"type":"message","id":"1f774b69","parentId":"0dae173c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:45:33.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK I think the MiniMax music-2.6 model is just timing out consistently. But the API auth is working (empty body returned 400, not auth error). So the key works, but the music generation for paid model is either too slow or there's an account configuration issue.\n\nLet me try one more thing - maybe MiniMax requires the `Content-Type` to be different, or maybe I need to use a different API format.\n\nActually, let me try with timeout just for the connection phase.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_DqdZTSm8OvIx5VtMVisM6749","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Quick connection check - just see if the server responds\ncurl -s -w \"\\nHTTP_CODE:%{http_code}\\nTIME:%{time_total}\" \\\n  --connect-timeout 10 --max-time 10 \\\n  -X POST \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-cp-…0lVY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"music-2.6\",\"prompt\":\"test\",\"is_instrumental\":true,\"output_format\":\"url\"}' 2>&1","timeout":15},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Quick connection check - just see if the server responds\\ncurl -s -w \\\"\\\\nHTTP_CODE:%{http_code}\\\\nTIME:%{time_total}\\\" \\\\\\n  --connect-timeout 10 --max-time 10 \\\\\\n  -X POST \\\"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer sk-cp-…0lVY\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\\"model\\\":\\\"music-2.6\\\",\\\"prompt\\\":\\\"test\\\",\\\"is_instrumental\\\":true,\\\"output_format\\\":\\\"url\\\"}' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 15}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":62,"output":371,"cacheRead":140544,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":103,"totalTokens":140977,"cost":{"input":0.00000868,"output":0.00010388