{"type":"message","id":"5ee8d177","parentId":"69421e07","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:45:50.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It seems to have died on its own. Let me just tell 汀桑 the situation honestly.\n\nThe API key is valid (empty request returns 400), but when we submit a proper music generation request with `music-2.6`, the server just hangs without returning anything. This could be because:\n1. The music model needs some pre-processing or queue time\n2. There might be an account configuration issue\n3. The model might not be available in his region\n\nLet me try one thing - maybe I need to set up a webhook/async pattern for MiniMax.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"API key 本身是通的（空请求马上返回 400），但每次提交实际音乐生成请求（`music-2.6`）都一直挂在那不返回——等了 5 分钟也没动静。\n\n可能原因：\n1. MiniMax 音乐生成可能要走异步回调模式，不是直接等同步返回\n2. 或者这个 key 的积分账户对 Music 模型的权限还没完全开\n\n要不要你直接去 **minimaxi.com** 的网页端试试能不能生成音乐？那边如果能跑，说明是 API 配置问题；如果网页端也不行，那就是账户的问题。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":123,"output":245,"cacheRead":141056,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":119,"totalTokens":141424,"cost":{"input":0.00001722,"output":0.0000686,"cacheRead":0.003949568,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004035388}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780231546266,"responseId":"a95d75fe-1214-4bbe-8336-ed14616d4fdd"}}
