{"type":"message","id":"4ace58c9","parentId":"7d3f49c3","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:46:04.341Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑告诉我了——我一直在请求生成音乐，但没设置时长。默认可能 AI 生成了一首完整的歌（几分钟长），所以一直在等。他问\"你直接让生成五分钟的歌吗\"。\n\n看看 API 文档里有没有 duration 参数来控制生成时长...\n\n实际上在之前的 API 文档里，`audio_setting` 对象可能包含 duration 设置。我记得我试过 `audio_setting: { duration: 15 }` 但那次也超时了。\n\n但汀桑说得对——我没有指定时长，默认可能生成很长的歌。应该设个短时长的测试，比如 15 秒。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈哈 好像真是——我没设时长，默认可能生成了完整的一首歌。再试一次，设 15 秒。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_cphIeqz8LasyTqlohdMK9170","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 30 -X POST \\\n  \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer ***…0lVY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"music-2.6\",\n    \"prompt\": \"轻快的夏日吉他曲\",\n    \"is_instrumental\": true,\n    \"output_format\": \"url\",\n    \"lyrics_optimizer\": false,\n    \"audio_setting\": {\n      \"duration\": 10\n    }\n  }' 2>&1","timeout":35},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"curl -s --max-time 30 -X POST \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer ***…0lVY\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\n    \\\"model\\\": \\\"music-2.6\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"轻快的夏日吉他曲\\\",\\n    \\\"is_instrumental\\\": true,\\n    \\\"output_format\\\": \\\"url\\\",\\n    \\\"lyrics_optimizer\\\": false,\\n    \\\"audio_setting\\\": {\\n      \\\"duration\\\": 10\\n    }\\n  }' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 35}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":7259,"output":356,"cacheRead":133248,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":134,"totalTokens":140863,"cost":{"input":0.0010162600000000002,"output":0.00009968000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003730944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004846884}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780231559211,"responseId":"4892