{"type":"message","id":"0399ce77","parentId":"f0274e65","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:51:13.682Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说 MiniMax 的音乐生成 \"只能在网页上单独使用\" - 他可能去看了 MiniMax 控制台，发现这个 API key 只能在网页端用，不支持 API 调用，或者积分模式的 key 和 API 调用的 key 是分开的。\n\n或者他的意思是 MiniMax 的音乐生成功能只能在网页上操作，不能通过 API 调用（或者积分用户没有 API 权限）。\n\n既然 MiniMax 的 API 调不通，那就回到阿里云百炼的 fun-music-v1 试试？之前阿里那个 key (sk-ff3...e82b) 报的是 InvalidApiKey 但可能是 endpoint 不对。让我试试正确的 endpoint。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"那 MiniMax 那边先放放。回阿里试试 `fun-music-v1`——之前 InvalidApiKey 可能是 endpoint 没找对。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Fqsjb0AletHPxonqloXb0769","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 60 -X POST \\\n  \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/audio/music/generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer ***…e82b\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"fun-music-v1\",\n    \"input\": {\n      \"prompt\": \"轻快的夏日吉他曲，放松心情，阳光沙滩\",\n      \"gender\": \"female\"\n    }\n  }' 2>&1","timeout":65},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"curl -s --max-time 60 -X POST \\\\\\n  \\\"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/audio/music/generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer ***…e82b\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\n    \\\"model\\\": \\\"fun-music-v1\\\",\\n    \\\"input\\\": {\\n      \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"轻快的夏日吉他曲，放松心情，阳光沙滩\\\",\\n      \\\"gender\\\": \\\"female\\\"\\n    }\\n  }' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 65}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":8950,"output":351,"cacheRead":140160,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":143,"totalTokens":149461,"cost":{"input":0.001253,"output":0.00009828,"cacheRead":0.00392448,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00527576}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780231869234,"responseId":"03fb15c7-d3c2-48c3-b4db-cc413ddfaa65"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8d185bb","parentId":"0399ce77","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:51:14.535Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Fqsjb0AletHPxonqloXb0769","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"code\":\"InvalidApiKey\",\"message\":\"Invalid API-key provided.\",\"request_id\":\"d5fda139-064a-97c9-9307-2dd978d502f6\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":369,"aggregated":"{\"code\":\"InvalidApiKey\",\"message\":\"Invalid API-key provided.\",\"request_id\":\"d5fda139-064a-97c9-9307-2dd978d502f6\"}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780231874534}}
{"type":"message","id":"d997041e","parentId":"b8d185bb","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:51:17.200Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"阿里百炼的 fun-music-v1 确实跟画图的 key 不通用——还是 InvalidApiKey。\n\n看来阿里和 MiniMax 两边的音乐生成 API 都需要单独的 key 或者权限。\n\n要不要我查查别的国内音乐生成 API？或者干脆先不管音乐这功能了，等以后有好用的再配。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"阿里那边也不行，fun-music-v1 要单独的 key。\n\n两个路都堵了：\n- **阿里 fun-music-v1** → 你这 key 没开音乐权限\n- **MiniMax music-2.6** → 积分用户 API 调用有限制，只能在网页用\n\n要不等你搞到能跑 API 的 key 再配？或者我查查还有没有别的国内音乐生成 API 能接。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":139,"output":163,"cacheRead":149376,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":69,"totalTokens":149678,"cost":{"input":0.00001946,"output":0.000045640000000000003,"cacheRead":0.004182528,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004247628}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780231874561,"responseId":"0e3bfe21-05c0-4793-afa9-e175fff12f00"}}
