{"type":"message","id":"659f5d1d","parentId":"1da9e874","timestamp":"2026-05-31T12:56:05.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑发了他的 conversation/sender metadata 和一个新的 MiniMax API key。他经常一起发送这些信息。\n\n这次他发的 key 跟之前的不一样——是完整的一长串：`sk-cp-…0Y98`\n\n这是他新生成的 API key。让我更新 env 并测试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"新 key 拿到了，完整的。换上试试。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_nM61LLidMyCnGDEFwd9x8700","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/.env << 'ENVEOF'\nexport MINIMAX_API_KEY=\"sk-cp-…0Y98\"\nENVEOF\necho \"done\"\n\n# Test with empty body to check auth\ncurl -s --max-time 10 -X POST \\\n  \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-cp-…0Y98\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{}' 2>&1","timeout":15},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat > /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/.env << 'ENVEOF'\\nexport MINIMAX_API_KEY=\\\"sk-cp-…0Y98\\\"\\nENVEOF\\necho \\\"done\\\"\\n\\n# Test with empty body to check auth\\ncurl -s --max-time 10 -X POST \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer sk-cp-…0Y98\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{}' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 15}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1081,"output":489,"cacheRead":148736,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":141,"totalTokens":150306,"cost":{"input":0.00015134,"output":0.00013692,"cacheRead":0.004164608,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0044528680000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780232159680,"responseId":"03434fdc-915f-4742-a69a-16db4b6f862a"}}
