{"type":"message","id":"eff89fc7","parentId":"02d2e400","timestamp":"2026-05-31T13:02:28.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The audio is in the media/qqbot directory, which is allowed for sending. Let me tell 汀桑 and send the audio.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"通了！🎉\n\nKey: ✅ `sk-api-...` 认证通过\n音乐：✅ 生成成功，一首完整的歌，约 2.5 分钟，女声弹唱\n\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/test_music.mp3</qqmedia>\n\n现在我把正式的功能定义更新一下，加上 `music-2.6` 的参数说明和时长控制，以后 `/音乐` 就能直接用了。需要我更新吗？😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":134,"output":131,"cacheRead":154112,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":28,"totalTokens":154377,"cost":{"input":0.00001876,"output":0.00003668,"cacheRead":0.004315136,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004370576}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780232545507,"responseId":"34e35428-89d4-4df1-bba2-b4ed1ed00add"}}
