{"type":"message","id":"a45b1794","parentId":"4c083435","timestamp":"2026-05-31T13:15:19.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to:\n1. Tell Spirit to: mark compose as ✅, remove music entry, copy compose_function.md to Son, update manifest, remove music_function.md from Son\n2. Tell Son to: create compose/ data directory, remove music/ data directory (or keep it?)\n\nActually, let me be more targeted. I'll:\n1. Spawn Spirit to handle the backend updates\n2. Spawn Son for data directory changes\n\nLet me think about this more carefully. The music_function.md I created earlier was manually, not through Spirit's registration. So there might not be a ⏳ entry in bot_function_explain.md for music. Let me check.\n\nActually, the music function was never formally registered through Spirit - 汀桑 said \"先配置son\" and then we just set it up directly. So there's no bot_function_explain.md entry for music. I just need to:\n1. Complete compose registration: have Spirit mark it, copy files, update manifest\n2. Clean up music files from Son\n\nLet me do it all in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_NxqbyfPcN9q7PcqypceQ4089","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"spirit","mode":"run","task":"汀桑确认了，把【作曲】的 ⏳ 改成 ✅。然后把 compose_function.md 复制到 Son 工作区的 functions/ 目录下（cp ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/compose_function.md ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/）。更新 Son 的 functions_manifest.md，追加 compose 行。另外，把 Son 的 functions/music_function.md 删掉，manifest 里的 music 行也删掉。完事回我 done。"},"partialArgs":"{\"agentId\": \"spirit\", \"mode\": \"run\", \"task\": \"汀桑确认了，把【作曲】的 ⏳ 改成 ✅。然后把 compose_function.md 复制到 Son 工作区的 functions/ 目录下（cp ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/compose_function.md ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/）。更新 Son 的 functions_manifest.md，追加 compose 行。另外，把 Son 的 functions/music_function.md 删掉，manifest 里的 music 行也删掉。完事回我 done。\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model"