{"type":"message","id":"64382a6a","parentId":"6c7a01e8","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:00:30.951Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Even the empty body returns 1004 now. Earlier the same key returned 2013 \"invalid params\" for empty body. This means the key has been invalidated or rotated, or the API call limit has been reached.\n\nSince汀桑 just sent the same key earlier and it worked, maybe the key has a usage limit that was exhausted by the previous successful generation (which generated a 2.5 minute song consuming some credits).\n\nLet me tell汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这个 key 现在也报 1004 了——可能刚才生成那首歌把额度用完了，或者 key 被轮换了。\n\n你还有没有别的 `sk-api-` 开头的 key？或者去控制台看看这个 key 的剩余额度是不是光了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":57,"output":152,"cacheRead":166656,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":94,"totalTokens":166865,"cost":{"input":0.00000798,"output":0.000042560000000000006,"cacheRead":0.004666368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004716908}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780236027455,"responseId":"fe9d9dd8-eb92-404c-b365-62506e886164"}}
