{"type":"message","id":"578922b3","parentId":"f048465b","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:01:41.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"2013 \"invalid params\" — key 认证通过！现在试试生成你的那首歌。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"key 通了！现在拿你的歌词生成看看。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HCRslD2bKMvgXoLwEs2k6215","name":"exec","arguments":{"background":true,"command":"curl -s --max-time 300 -X POST \\\n  \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-api…adXE\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"music-2.6\",\n    \"prompt\": \"电子音乐，Joji风格，空灵忧郁，氛围感，迷幻电子节奏，中速\",\n    \"lyrics\": \"漆黑的风涌来，吹灭最后一道黎明，落下万千星辰。\\n我挥动古老的船桨，从亿万的时间赶来。\\n看那倏生倏灭的斑斓，凝结成幽蓝的水晶。\\n我曾与谁同行？谁可曾向我呼唤？\\n记忆清晰而陌生。\\n那座殿堂永远伫立，那些原野，那些小镇，\\n随着黄昏的曲调而永恒。\\n可我为何长怀遗憾？\\n便穿过先祖赐予灵魂的沟壑，欣喜地游离时空的尽头。\",\n    \"lyrics_optimizer\": false,\n    \"is_instrumental\": false,\n    \"output_format\": \"url\"\n  }' 2>&1","timeout":310},"partialArgs":"{\"background\": true, \"command\": \"curl -s --max-time 300 -X POST \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer sk-api…adXE\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\n    \\\"model\\\": \\\"music-2.6\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"电子音乐，Joji风格，空灵忧郁，氛围感，迷幻电子节奏，中速\\\",\\n    \\\"lyrics\\\": \\\"漆黑的风涌来，吹灭最后一道黎明，落下万千星辰。\\\\n我挥动古老的船桨，从亿万的时间赶来。\\\\n看那倏生倏灭的斑斓，凝结成幽蓝的水晶。\\\\n我曾与谁同行？谁可曾向我呼唤？\\\\n记忆清晰而陌生。\\\\n那座殿堂永远伫立，那些原野，那些小镇，\\\\n随着黄昏的曲调而永恒。\\\\n可我为何长怀遗憾？\\\\n便穿过先祖赐予灵魂的沟壑，欣喜地游离时空的尽头。\\\",\\n    \\\"lyrics_optimizer\\\": false,\\n    \\\"is_instrumental\\\": false,\\n    \\\"output_format\\\": \\\"url\\\"\\n  }' 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 310}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":74,"output":448,"cacheRead":167424,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":19,"totalTokens":167946,"cost":{"input":0.00001036,"output":0.00012544000000000002,"cache