{"type":"message","id":"d291e597","parentId":"6a4e35ef","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:07:53.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, .m4a is also an audio format, it would still be recognized as voice. Let me check the skill doc again:\n\n```\n`.jpg/.png/.gif/.webp/.bmp` → 图片\n`.silk/.wav/.mp3/.ogg/.aac/.flac` 等 → 语音\n`.mp4/.mov/.avi/.mkv/.webm` 等 → 视频\n其他扩展名 → 文件\n```\n\nSo I need an extension that is NOT in any of these lists. `.m4a` is not listed, but it might still be recognized as audio by the system. Let me try with a completely different extension like `.bin` or `.dat` which would be classified as \"文件\".\n\nActually, the best approach might be to just rename it without a recognized audio extension so it falls through to \"文件\".","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_0jaMSOEQAIIsIut49bkJ2851","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.mp3 /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.mp3.bin\nls -lh /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.mp3.bin"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cp /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.mp3 /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.mp3.bin\\nls -lh /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.mp3.bin\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":86,"output":278,"cacheRead":170624,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":182,"totalTokens":170988,"cost":{"input":0.000012040000000000002,"output":0.00007784,"cacheRead":0.004777472,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004867351999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780236469952,"responseId":"85ec6637-1e5a-487c-8a89-05f35b7b876c"}}
