{"type":"message","id":"7de84393","parentId":"51ea401f","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:07:57.604Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `.bin` extension is not in any of the recognized media lists, so it should be sent as a \"文件\" (file). Let me send this instead.\n\nBut I realize the user will have to rename it to .mp3 to play it. Maybe I should note that.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"对，我这边发的是 mp3，但 QQ Bot 自动把它转成语音消息了。我改成文件形式试试。\n\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.mp3.bin</qqmedia>\n\n收到后改成 `.mp3` 就能播了。或者下次我直接改`.music`扩展名发给你当文件，你改回.mp3听。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":158,"output":144,"cacheRead":170880,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":58,"totalTokens":171182,"cost":{"input":0.00002212,"output":0.00004032,"cacheRead":0.00478464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00484708}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780236474579,"responseId":"b57b174f-a6b0-43b9-a529-8fdb734b7ec8"}}
