{"type":"message","id":"f8fdc68e","parentId":"fa9919c8","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:15:20.828Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说 `m4a` 格式可能是完美符合他需求的。之前我试过 `.m4a` 但当时我以为是同样的音频格式也会走语音通道。但他这么说，让我试试m4a。\n\n查看 qqbot-media skill 文档的分类：\n- `.silk/.wav/.mp3/.ogg/.aac/.flac` 等 → 语音\n\n`.m4a` 不在这个列表里！所以我之前错误地认为m4a会被识别为语音，但实际上它可能被归类为\"文件\"！\n\n让我试试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"之前我试了 `.m4a` 但以为也会被当语音。`.m4a` 不再语音识别列表里，应该能当文件推送！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_r7YSu4dg0Yn240wj1WUN1387","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.mp3 /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.m4a\nls -lh /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.m4a"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cp /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.mp3 /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.m4a\\nls -lh /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/compose_test.m4a\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3545,"output":247,"cacheRead":176128,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":119,"totalTokens":179920,"cost":{"input":0.0004963000000000001,"output":0.00006916000000000001,"cacheRead":0.004931584,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005497044}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780236917302,"responseId":"26f7cb3d-1260-4620-bc83-41e9ba39be00"}}
