{"type":"message","id":"fb256cba","parentId":"4f2caf0a","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:18:57.414Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说\"不行\" - 所以.mp4伪装成视频也不行。\n\n我直接跟他说明情况吧。目前OpenClaw的`<qqmedia>`对音频文件没有\"强制以文件形式发送\"的选项。最佳方案就是伪装成.bin文件让他自己改后缀。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"确实——mp3 套 mp4 皮 QQ 也播不了😅\n\n现在的情况是：\n\n| 方式 | 结果 |\n|:----|:----|\n| `.mp3` → `<qqmedia>` | 语音消息，不能保存转发 |\n| `.m4a` → `<qqmedia>` | 同上 |\n| `.mp4` 伪装 | 播不了 |\n| `.bin` / `.music` | 文件消息，能下载保存，但得手动改后缀 |\n\n目前就两种选择：\n1. **`.bin` 发你**，下载后改 `.mp3` 就能播\n2. **等以后** OpenClaw 支持强制指定媒体类型\n\n你倾向哪个？😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":869,"output":215,"cacheRead":179712,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":60,"totalTokens":180796,"cost":{"input":0.00012166000000000001,"output":0.000060200000000000006,"cacheRead":0.005031936,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005213796}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780237133546,"responseId":"be0962a2-d117-4207-af60-551425ae3e87"}}
