{"type":"message","id":"e09921b6","parentId":"ca0e9ca9","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:29:56.454Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now the compose function has clear logic for handling lyrics_optimizer. Let me also update the return format to include the full lyrics when they're available. Actually, the format already has `📝 歌词：{lyrics_preview}` in section 6.1, so that should be fine as long as Son includes the lyrics in the result.\n\nLet me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"改好了。逻辑变这样：\n\n| 情况 | `lyrics_optimizer` | 歌词来源 |\n|:----|:------------------:|:--------:|\n| 你传了歌词 | `false` | 你的原词 |\n| 你没传歌词 | `true` | AI 根据 prompt 自动写词 |\n\n刚才那首就是 `false`，但你给 Son 的歌词没被正确提取，所以我回你的时候也没贴回来。下次 `/作曲` 流程通的话，歌词会正常带上了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":140,"output":194,"cacheRead":186496,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":81,"totalTokens":186830,"cost":{"input":0.000019600000000000002,"output":0.00005432,"cacheRead":0.005221888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005295808}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780237793100,"responseId":"c54a5a16-fff2-48ed-807f-daf0ec3f8413"}}
