{"type":"message","id":"6fa6a7d5","parentId":"803899cd","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:37:44.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both files exist. Let me present the result with the polished lyrics and both media links.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🎵 **黎明之前闭上眼** — #polish 版完成！\n────────────────\n🎸 new jazz + hiphop | 💖 温柔怀旧 | ⏱ 4:02\n\n**润色后歌词：**\n```\n风穿过街道 回忆里穿梭\n梧桐道光影斑驳\n平凡的午后藏着梦\n阳光撒落一地琥珀\n\n背上的奶瓶摇摇晃\n配送员脚步轻放\n拂晓前街巷湿又长\n怕惊扰谁家好梦乡\n巷路蜿蜒向上行\n消失在黎明的殿堂\n\n......\n\n徘徊踱步何时到\n小镇尽头通云霄\n黎明之前闭上眼微笑\n```\n\n**🎧 直接听：**\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260531-0002.mp3</qqmedia>\n\n**📦 保存转发（改.mp3）：**\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260531-0002.mp3.bin</qqmedia>\n\n押韵和 flow 都润过了——原版的叙事感保留，但更顺嘴了👊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":139,"output":256,"cacheRead":191488,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":18,"totalTokens":191883,"cost":{"input":0.00001946,"output":0.00007168,"cacheRead":0.0053616639999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0054528039999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780238261240,"responseId":"e5ed263d-a742-4525-b788-debb561f289f"}}
