{"type":"message","id":"1fecb74c","parentId":"187f04ed","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:40:38.712Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_nqG453EWdof73qTV0HwG4635","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/compose_function.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  23 Son 执行步骤:\n  24 1. 从 params.lyrics 提取歌词文本（如果有）\n  25 2. 从 params.style / params.mood / params.tempo 提取风格/情绪/节奏参数\n  26 3. 若用户描述中未提供风格/情绪，则根据歌词内容自动推断\n- 27 4. 检查 prompt 中是否包含控制标签：\n+ 27 4. 判断是否纯音乐：如果用户未传 lyrics（或歌词为空）且不带 #polish / #auto_lyrics → `is_instrumental: true`（纯音乐）；如果用户传了 lyrics → `is_instrumental: false`（带人声）\n+ 28 5. 检查 prompt 中是否包含控制标签：\n  28    - `#auto_lyrics`：忽略 params.lyrics，清空 lyrics，设 `lyrics_optimizer: true`，让 AI 完全重写歌词\n  29    - `#polish`：将 params.lyrics 发给 LLM 做押韵/节奏润色，润色后的歌词传给 API，`lyrics_optimizer: false`\n  30    - 无标签且 params.lyrics 存在 → 直接用原词，`lyrics_optimizer: false`\n  31    - 无标签且 params.lyrics 为空 → `lyrics_optimizer: true`，AI 自动写词\n     ...","patch":"--- /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/compose_function.md\n+++ /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/compose_function.md\n@@ -23,9 +23,10 @@\n Son 执行步骤:\n 1. 从 params.lyrics 提取歌词文本（如果有）\n 2. 从 params.style / params.mood / params.tempo 提取风格/情绪/节奏参数\n 3. 若用户描述中未提供风格/情绪，则根据歌词内容自动推断\n-4. 检查 prompt 中是否包含控制标签：\n+4. 判断是否纯音乐：如果用户未传 lyrics（或歌词为空）且不带 #polish / #auto_lyrics → `is_instrumental: true`（纯音乐）；如果用户传了 lyrics → `is_instrumental: false`（带人声）\n+5. 检查 prompt 中是否包含控制标签：\n    - `#auto_lyrics`：忽略 params.lyrics，清空 lyrics，设 `lyrics_optimizer: true`，让 AI 完全重写歌词\n    - `#polish`：将 params.lyrics 发给 LLM 做押韵/节奏润色，润色后的歌词传给 API，`lyrics_optimizer: false`\n    - 无标签且 params.lyrics 存在 → 直接用原词，`lyrics_optimizer: false`\n    - 无标签且 params.lyrics 为空 → `lyrics_optimizer: true`，AI 自动写词\n","firstChangedLine":27},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780238438711}}
{"type":"message","id":"04b09796","parentId":"1fecb74c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:40:45.421Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now the logic is:\n- No lyrics provided → pure instrumental (`is_instrumental: true`)\n- Lyrics provided → with vocals (`is_instrumental: false`)\n\nThis makes sense. For汀桑's first request, he provided lyrics AND expected instrumental - which is a contradiction with how the API works. If you provide lyrics and set is_instrumental to true, MiniMax would ignore the lyrics entirely.\n\nActually wait - 汀桑说\"原曲是纯音乐来着\" - the previous version (\"风与黎明\") was generated WITH vocals because I didn't set is_instrumental. But he wanted it as pure instrumental.\n\nBut he also provided lyrics for that request... Hmm, if it's pure instrumental, the lyrics wouldn't be sung. Maybe he wants instrumental that follows the mood of the lyrics.\n\nActually, MiniMax API docs say:\n- `is_instrumental: true` + lyrics → MiniMax ignores lyrics, generates pure music based on prompt only\n- `is_instrumental: false` + lyrics → sings the lyrics\n\nSo if he wants pure instrumental but also wants the lyrics... that's contradictory. But he might want instrumental music that captures the vibe of the lyrics, without singing.\n\nFor the first version (COMPOSE-20260531-0001), I sent `is_instrumental: false` + lyrics → so it sang the full lyrics. Now he's saying he wanted pure instrumental.\n\nFor the second version #polish (COMPOSE-20260531-0002), same thing - it also sang with vocals.\n\nOK so the issue is: he wants the vibe of the lyrics but as instrumental music. The current logic I just wrote (no lyrics → instrumental, has lyrics → vocals) is actually reasonable. But he specifically wants instrumental even with lyrics.\n\nMaybe I should add a tag for that too - `#instrumental` to force instrumental even with lyrics.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"等等，你说第一次那首风与黎明你本来想要的是**纯音乐**？但你传了歌词啊——\n\n纯音乐（`is_instrumental: true`）的话，MiniMax 会直接忽略歌词，只根据 prompt 生成伴奏。歌词不会被唱出来。\n\n你是想要**有伴奏没人声**，但歌词还是要写出来作为情绪参考？那我可以加个 **`#instrumental`** 标签，强制纯音乐但不丢歌词文本展示给你看。要加吗？👊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":118,"output":500,"cacheRead":191872,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":392,"totalTokens":192490,"cost":{"input":0.00001652,"output":0.00014000000000000001,"cacheRead":0.005372416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005528936}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780238438765,"responseId":"fdd80ba9-c2b2-44ad-a7d3-2f78cf3dbf41"}}
