{"type":"message","id":"4c5af181","parentId":"9f273c3c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:55:32.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still \"login fail\" for `music-2.6-free`. This key's plan doesn't support the free model.\n\n汀桑说\"一首一块钱\"——意思是每次调用 `music-2.6` 付费版大概扣 1 块钱。他觉得应该有免费额度可以用。\n\n现在的问题是这个 key `sk-api-...adXE` 的 API 套餐不支持免费模型。汀桑可能需要在 MiniMax 控制台换个套餐或者生成一个专门用于 free 模型的 key。\n\n不过说实话，MiniMax 的免费额度可能只送了一次（新用户注册），用完就没了。加上他这个 `sk-api-` key 可能本身就不是免费计划的 key。\n\n让我告诉汀桑现状。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"还是 1004——这个 key 的套餐不让你用免费模型。\n\n一首一块钱是因为走的 `music-2.6` 付费版。你现在两个选择：\n\n1. **继续用 `music-2.6`** — 一首约 1 块，效果你听到了\n2. **去 MiniMax 控制台看看免费额度** — 新用户注册送的那些免费次数可能是绑在网页端的，不是这个 API key。或者看看能不能生成一个**专门给免费模型用的 API Key**\n\n你那个 `sk-cp-` 开头的积分 key 能调通吗？还是说积分只能在网页上用？🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":170,"output":284,"cacheRead":204672,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":146,"totalTokens":205126,"cost":{"input":0.000023800000000000003,"output":0.00007952000000000001,"cacheRead":0.005730816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005834135999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780239328562,"responseId":"0f9f96e2-8d2b-41c6-bc86-5aeb5dc970ba"}}
{"type":"message","id":"655f70ba","parentId":"4c5af181","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:59:45.381Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"There was once a prince\nPinioned to cliff,bound by shackles\nIn the mountains,up on the summit\nTremble every night\nIn his tattered clothes\nWhen the winter days fall\n\nCascading snowflakes\nTravelled through the long trek\nBefore their wedding with the ground\nAll fell on the prince\nMingled with the drudge\nThat odorous ooze\nfollowing the track of seasons\n\nHow they saturated his back\nMelting in his remained warmth\nAnd sweltered him\nIn the reverse baptism\nBefore they all became cold\n\nBeware to take a retro\nChurning flakes,and whizzing sight\nHow they rewind\nLike a cassette strap\nUntil only retained in memories’ mind\n\nAdvent of an angel\nFrom the lustrous heaven\nThe words descend\n\nPrince,for a long time you have suffered\nWith manacles, In those chilling night\nNever retrieve the drumsticks\nDown in the dungeon,deeper than any dream\nSpindled cloisters\nYet you creep,yet you cry\nHow you shiver with affright\nTo the core of naught alike\n\nCome with me\nOn the pilgrimage to spring\nWhere you find the snow puffy\nAnd the flowers jolly","timestamp":1780239583272}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d9de949","parentId":"655f70ba","timestamp":"2026-05-31T14:59:51.318Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑发了一段很长的英文诗（或者歌词），以及一些系统metadata。这是他的新歌词，可能是想让我创作成歌。\n\n这看起来像是一首关于被锁在悬崖上的王子的英文诗，风格很哥特/梦幻。\n\n他之前问了关于音乐生成免费额度的问题，我回答了。现在他发了这首诗，应该是想让我用 MiniMax 来作曲。\n\n不过这个歌词挺长的，风格应该是那种史诗感的。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这首诗是你写的？英文有点味道👊\n\n**\"There was once a prince, pinioned to cliff, bound by shackles...\"** ——氛围拉满了。\n\n要我用 MiniMax 给它作曲吗？什么风格？**epic orchestral**？**dark ambient**？**cinematic**？😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2003,"output":158,"cacheRead":203392,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":92,"totalTokens":205553,"cost":{"input":0.00028042000000000003,"output":0.00004424,"cacheRead":0.005694976,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006019636}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780239585437,"responseId":"5fb53812-4924-4248-a7bf-491582ee521b"}}
