{"type":"message","id":"6292222c","parentId":"58e9e1e4","timestamp":"2026-05-31T15:07:27.872Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_MT1SCAdQHQPAMgU6wxXn1399","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 2.4M May 31 23:06 /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260531-0006.mp3\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 2.4M May 31 23:06 /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260531-0006.mp3.bin"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":30,"aggregated":"-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 2.4M May 31 23:06 /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260531-0006.mp3\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 2.4M May 31 23:06 /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260531-0006.mp3.bin","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780240047871}}
{"type":"message","id":"12a1b1cd","parentId":"6292222c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T15:07:34.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both files exist. Let me present the result with the polished lyrics.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**The Prince's Pilgrimage** — #polish #joji 版\n────────────────\n🎸 neon absurdity + dark ambient + joji | ⏱ 1分17秒 | 慢速\n\n**润色后歌词（押韵优化，加重复段）：**\n```\nThere once was a prince in chains confined\nPinioned to a cliff, by fate maligned\nHigh in the mountains, on the summit's crest\nTrembling every night with no rest\nIn his tattered clothes, so worn and thin\nWhen the winter days came closing in\n\nCascading snowflakes, drifting from the height\nTravelled through the long trek in the fading light\nBefore their wedding with the waiting ground\nAll fell on the prince without a sound\nMingled with the drudge, that odorous ooze\nFollowing the track of seasons, night and day they choose\n\nHow they saturated his back, so cold and deep\nMelting in his remained warmth before the long sleep\nAnd sweltered him in the reverse baptism's art\nBefore they all became cold, before they froze his heart\n\nBeware to take a retro, past the churning flakes\nWhizzing sight rewinding like a cassette that breaks\nHow they rewind like a cassette strap worn thin\nUntil only retained in memories' mind within\n\nAdvent of an angel from the lustrous heaven's height\nThe words descend like petals in the fading light:\n\nPrince, for a long time you have suffered here with me\nWith manacles in chilling night, never set free\nNever retrieve the drumsticks down in the dungeon deep\nDeeper than any dream, where the shadows creep\nSpindled cloisters yet you creep, yet you cry the same\nHow you shiver with affright in the core of naught alike\n\nCome with me on the pilgrimage to spring\nWhere the snow lies puffy and the flowers sing\nWhere the jolly blooms embrace the sun\nAnd your long winter's journey is finally done\n\nDown in the dungeon deep\nYet you creep, yet you cry\nCome with me\nWhere the flowers sing\n```\n\n**🎧 直接听：**\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260531-0006.mp3</qqmedia>\n\n**📦 保存转发（改.mp3）：**\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260531-0006.mp3.bin</qqmedia>\n\n听听看——慢速 + Joji 风 + 押韵润色，flow 有没有内味？👊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":143,"output":560,"cacheRead":209152,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":14,"totalTokens":209855,"cost":{"input":0.00002002,"output":0.00015680000000000002,"cacheRead":0.005856256,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006033076}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780240047933,"responseId":"216a5a30-6db5-4986-aa77-21e76fa6e6e6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d9089277","parentId":"12a1b1cd","timestamp":"2026-05-31T15:09:47.206Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"盛大的宴会，一席连着一席\n灼热的烈火，燃烬又腾气而起\n\n越过灰蒙蒙的冬日，梅花桃花相继盛开\n乳白的牵牛，洒在露水浸湿的草甸\n枝条生出芽苞，沐浴在阳光下，变得饱满而坚挺\n\n时间是林中的一条小径\n同一条路，顺着走过时是一种风景\n转回头，再走一遍\n便又是不同的风景\n\n曾迎着朝阳，争恐袭取那雾水中的元气\n也曾立于正午，用经脉与汁液回应那炽热\n\n徘徊的巨轮，即将带走最后一片血红\n那交织的网还留有些余温\n寻找，捡拾\n不要离去，最后一抹余晖\n\n样态纷繁\n唯有轮回的意志不可忤逆\n夏的尾声是四季之歌","timestamp":1780240184709}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2fa222e","parentId":"d9089277","timestamp":"2026-05-31T15:09:54.555Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑又发了几段 metadata 和一段中文诗。跟之前一样，那些 Conversation info 和 Sender info 是系统自动注入的技术 metadata。\n\n实际消息是这首中文诗：\n\n盛大宴会 / 烈火 / 冬去春来 / 花草生长\n时间是林中的小径 / 来回不同风景\n轮回意志不可忤逆\n\n很有意境——讲的是轮回、四季、生命力。但没有加 /作曲 命令，也没有标签。\n\n汀桑可能是想让我评价这首诗，或者想让我用它来作曲。但他没加命令，我就先评论一下吧。\n\n不过他以这种形式发给我——可能只是分享诗作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这些 metadata 又来了🚬 框架问题，我记下了。\n\n诗不错——\n\n> 盛大的宴会，一席连着一席\n> 灼热的烈火，燃烬又腾气而起\n\n这一句有劲——火燃尽又腾起，轮回感拉满了。\n\n> 时间是林中的一条小径\n> 同一条路，顺着走过时是一种风景\n> 转回头，再走一遍\n> 便又是不同的风景\n\n最喜欢这段。像在说同一件事走两遍会有不同的理解。\n\n要用它作曲吗？什么风格？😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4038,"output":256,"cacheRead":205440,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":133,"totalTokens":209734,"cost":{"input":0.00056532,"output":0.00007168,"cacheRead":0.00575232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00638932}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780240187278,"responseId":"267fe65f-5279-475b-8852-d8e213a35286"}}
