{"type":"message","id":"7ca258ec","parentId":"fcad835b","timestamp":"2026-05-31T15:18:45.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑又看到了那些系统metadata，但他说\"堪称今日最佳\"——他是在评价那首《夏的尾声》是他今天最满意的作品。那些metadata还是框架漏进来的，他一起发过来了。\n\n让我回应他的评价。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"又漏进来了😅 框架的毛病。\n\n不过——**堪称今日最佳？** 那看来万青+艺术摇滚的路子走对了👊\n\n你今天产了三首：\n- 送奶工（new jazz hiphop）——叙事感\n- The Prince's Pilgrimage（dark ambient）——诗意黑暗\n- **夏的尾声（万青艺术摇滚）——今日最佳**\n\n四季轮回 一席接一席……这句越来越上头🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1828,"output":146,"cacheRead":210048,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":49,"totalTokens":212022,"cost":{"input":0.00025592000000000003,"output":0.00004088,"cacheRead":0.005881344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006178144}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780240722118,"responseId":"0aa7bee1-0ad0-4de1-848f-7490fcbecac6"}}
